data.description: A rare find in one of Etown's most established neighborhoods. An all brick home with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bath and so much more.  Recent upgrades include new windows, new appliances, counter tops and sink (quartz) Updated flooring in upstairs bathrooms, laundry room and basement. Updated vanities and shower in upstairs bathroom.  Your welcomed into                                                                      the large entry way with hardwood flooring and 2 coat closets.  In the front of the home you will find the formal living and dining room. Across the back of the home are the oversized family room, opening to the kitchen with many upgrades. The upper level bedrooms are spacious with the master featuring a large walk in closet and an amazing bathroom. In the lower level a gathering area leading to a kitchenette and full bath.  Plenty of storage available.  From the deck you can view the 1/2 acre lot.
